Maintainer: Victoria Dominguez Almela <vda1r22@soton.ac.uk>
Description: A system for ecological and environmental users to build,
    visualise and evaluate Bayesian belief networks. These models can
    incorporate expert knowledge and/or empirical data to model complex
    systems.
